framework

Class Framework

  • java.lang.Object
    • framework.Framework

  • public class Framework
extends java.lang.Object
    Core Framework for running Keywords and PageObject repeatable methods Allows for Method Chaining Keyword and PageObject methods for simplified clean code
    Author:
    Mathew Carrigan

        public Framework withPageObject(CheckedRunnable func)

        Parameters:
